lpRules1: Mining rules: Pools that also meet the following 3 algorithm rules can open LP pool mining permissions on the next day
lpRules1-1: ①There is a token in the pool that is one of the 5 mainstream currencies: USDT, HUSD, HT, ETH, and BTC;
lpRules1-2: ②The liquidity value of the pool exceeds 100,000 USDT (the sum of the value of the two tokens is greater than or equal to 100,000 USDT);
lpRules1-3: ③3 consecutive days in the pool and the daily transaction fee exceeds 100USDT;
lpRules2: Profit rule: LP mining area accounts for 95% of the total coin production. The coin production coefficient between each pool depends on the transaction fee of the previous day. For details, please refer to the "coefficient" bullet window.
lpRules3: Delisting rule: When the LP liquidity pool has a single-day transaction fee of less than 100 USDT for multiple consecutive days, the LP mining area will be delisted.
lpRules4: Incentive object: The platform will give 2-3 times the mining coefficient incentive in the first week of the launch of the new project.
singleRules1: Token listing rules: Click to fill in the above application form, submit the project contract address, project introduction, LOGO and other main information, and then the single currency area will be launched within 24 hours.
singleRules2: Mining rules: pools that meet the following 3 rules at the same time can open single currency mining permissions on the next day
singleRules2-1: ①The value of the liquidity in the pool exceeds 10,000 USDT; and there is a handling fee of more than 100U;
singleRules2-2: ②Fill in the application form information completely;
singleRules2-3: ③After going online, the pledge address in the pool reaches 100 or more;
singleRules3: Revenue rules: The amount of coins produced in a single currency area accounts for 5% of the total amount of coins produced. The mining coefficient of each pool is calculated based on the number of staked addresses at 12:00 on the day. You can check the "Coefficient" pop-up window for details.
singleRules4: Removal rules: Adhering to the principle of fairness and justice, each pool that participates in the mining of a single currency zone has only one month of mining period.
singleRules5: Note: Because the coefficient of the single currency zone pool is determined by the number of addresses, in order to prevent malicious swiping of the number of addresses, 0.1HT is charged for each address pledge and withdrawal.
lpMiningTimeStart: Mining will officially start at 16:00 on March 26th, Beijing time. You can pledge in advance and wait for the mining to start!
